headline: Is Weyerhaeuser (WY) Pricing Look Interesting After Recent Share Price Volatility
summary: If you are wondering whether Weyerhaeuser is attractively priced right now, you are not alone. This article focuses squarely on what the current share price might be offering you as an investor. The stock most recently closed at US$25.93, after a mixed run that includes an 8.1% gain over the last 30 days, an 8.9% return year to date, but a 13.5% decline over the past year and an 18.7% and 6.6% decline over the last 3 and 5 years respectively.
